Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這藉口編得跟麻耶一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.80,0:00:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}有好多拿著花的高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}今天是高中的畢業典禮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.59,0:00:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}話說回來 志願該怎麼填呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.91,0:00:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}已經到了不得不考慮的時候了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:01:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}說到畢業典禮 心愛她…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還沒有畢業吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.10,0:01:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}能順利升班嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.97,0:01:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是在擔心這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我覺得沒問題喲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.18,0:01:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我只是說說看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃QAQ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真有問題啊！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}<OP>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}被畢業典禮感動到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}什麼嘛 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嚇了我們一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}而且 一想到我來到這個小鎮如今已經快一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}時間真是轉瞬即逝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 在這在這
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你怎麼哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你們是已經約好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 為了慶祝升班想開個茶會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}找到家不錯的咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃你們也一起來怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對別的店見異思遷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要從Rabbit House畢業了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不是的啦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\pos(640,643)\c&HB1FFFB&}心愛學姐優雅的茶會指導
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}滿座了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}和高中生組的座位分開了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我也想像那樣變得更加成熟些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}成熟些？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}像是對後輩說「一起去喝茶吧」這樣自然的邀請她們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}能不能很自然的邀請到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那麼惠 我們來試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來吧來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}做得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個 嗯哼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你 你真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一… 一起去喝茶怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是可疑的搭訕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哈哈哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紗路喝茶的樣子跟大小姐一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}感覺很成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我也想成為那樣的高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這個券還可以用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是免費券吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:05:00.70,Default,屏幕,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\bord0\c&H505366&\pos(565,460)\frz298.753}1杯免費券
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真是精打細算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}令人憧憬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}總覺得妹妹好像被人搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}有沒有成熟些了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}變得稍微優雅些了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是您的下午茶套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哦 好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我們沒點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是那邊的客人送的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這裡不是酒吧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯哼哼 看起來很高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是姐姐給可愛的妹妹們的禮物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}謝謝 心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我開動……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我聽說吃這些是有順序的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:05:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好像是從三明治開始的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}還是司康餅來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這要不吃出點樣子來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就沒法成為成熟的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}怎 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我們還是學學紗路她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}在吃熱狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對面也上來和我們一樣的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是模仿的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}盯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我感受到一股羡慕的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不 也許是我們正被觀察著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}觀察…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}觀察我們是不是值得尊敬的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}太誇張了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是嗎 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你信了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你們覺得我對相對論的說明好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是想展現自己的腦袋頂呱呱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要說到狹義相對論和廣義相對論的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我比較喜歡狹義相對論
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這話題竟然給接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這 這年頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}把般若心經背下不過是小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}連紗路也來！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}果然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}廣義
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}說到宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}狹義相對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}雖然搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不過應該是想在開吃之前好好聊一聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我們也得說些成熟的話題才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 最近我第一次讓老哥去幫我跑腿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這哪裡成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}下 下次我就去Rabbit House的酒吧逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我 我就熬一下夜試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐我是不會允許的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}被聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}在喝下午茶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}看起來好歡樂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}青山小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}您知道這東西的吃法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}普通地吃不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}普通？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對呀 普通地吃就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}青山小姐的普通估計和我們的不太一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}難道我很特殊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃她們在和青山小姐聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}話題好像挺嚴肅的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}她們肯定是在向青山小姐尋求意見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}關於什麼的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}經過她們的觀察覺得我們不值得尊敬什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}青山小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃她們要我來觀察觀察各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}別說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}相 相對論嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}狹義和廣義和…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}色 色即是空 空 空即是色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:09:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我 我比較喜歡宇宙弦理論
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}呀 真巧 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}大 大家都這樣嗎 好巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我也是 我挺喜歡宇宙弦理論的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}因為不知道下午茶怎麼喝才觀察的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}呃 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}學著學著你的動作就跟到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒必要這麼鑽牛角尖的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}可是 對於成熟的女性來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這些東西只要吃的開心就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}禮儀也只是為了讓彼此更舒暢才存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}教官之訓導 深入我心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 她們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}有空位子了所以拜託店員合併起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}鏘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}用抽籤來分位子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}可別為了自己和晚輩們坐一起出老千啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我可是很公平的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}人家光是能和大家一起開茶會就已經很高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這個好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}來 智乃也吃吃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯 也吃吃這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}只是分到了最遠的座位而已嘛 別這麼沮喪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好 好遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我有個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}什麼什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}儘管問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}狹義相對論和廣義相對論有什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}誰叫你們那麼逞能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我要更努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}嗯 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}再來再來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你到底想幹啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我要變得更有姐姐樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃 我來幫你拿書包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不 不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}和姐姐客氣什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我沒客氣什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那我來背你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}客氣什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是姐姐寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這次的回信速度好快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛 天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛 就算是春假也不能睡懶覺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}玩偶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}早安 智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}早飯要涼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}和平時不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是燒焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}用完早飯後　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我會告訴你狹義相對論和廣義相對論之間的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛的樣子很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}的確
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}比平時更加機敏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是在幹啥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}摸提比也摸地更加機敏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}攬客的動作也更機敏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}帶您入座
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好紳士～～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}搞得像別家店一樣了 請別繼續了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這麼一說和平時瀏海的方向也反過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}可能是冒充的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}毛茸茸 毛茸茸 毛茸茸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}毛茸茸天國！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這個應該還是會忍不住抱過來才對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不認真工作是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}雖然不知道為什麼但是非常不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}微妙的受挫感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}如果努力過頭發燒了就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我才剛這麼想！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}為什麼在這之前不說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}後天…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}後天？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐要過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就是說想讓姐姐看到自己努力的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要更加努力的去做才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要好好的做智乃的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛的姐姐很嚴厲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}安心啦 很溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}雖然我也有兩個哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是姐姐教訓他們 讓他們聽話的樣子很帥的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}教訓什麼的 她是馴獸師嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}調教 我接下來會被怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}發抖了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}原來如此 所以才憧憬著姐姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}身為老么也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好 我來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}讓她看看你的優點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是 好羡慕心愛有那麼多兄弟姐妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我是獨生女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}理世也要作為我的妹妹介紹給姐姐哦 和智乃一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}普通的朋友就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐修行？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}怎樣才能看起來很可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我想讓姐姐看到我的成長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}總之 先讓從剛才開始就抖個不停的智乃安下心來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be3}要被揉個不停了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒關係 有我陪著你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:15:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}沒～關係 有我陪著你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be3}住手 住手 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}明明是一樣的台詞 但差距這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}對了 理世你們稍微犯點蠢的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這樣就顯得心愛很可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}逆向思考？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}但是 已經說了要幫助她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}知道了 我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}咦咦咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那麼 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我想點餐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那個 咖 咖啡的種類我不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛 來幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我數學很爛 不小心訂了一噸的罐裝咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你這個冒失鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛 麵包能用火焰噴射器烤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}哇啊啊啊 我看不下去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這可是為了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}接下來該換我們上場了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}請多指教 Sir！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛 這裡還有灰塵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}感覺有什麼要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這是婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}要接住這個飛盤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}汪！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3\an8}好啦 我要扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}話說回來 這是什麼的特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}因為想變得像姐姐一樣 所以請模仿一下妹妹的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}姐姐 我想吃麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我 我也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}幫我做作業
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一會就來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這要持續到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}直到心愛察覺到這毫無意義為止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}今天謝謝大家為我忙這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}幾杯咖啡拿鐵 不成敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊 這是心愛畫的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}比我第一次給我的時候進步多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一直都在看反而沒發現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這不就是你有在成長的證明嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好棒好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}好 今後我會更加發奮的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我想看3D咖啡拉花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}就算作為店員進步了 作為姐姐也還差得很遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}3D咖啡拉花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}只是提比而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不管過多久都成不了一個可靠的姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是嗎？ 我覺得心愛已經是個很好的姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}雖說如此 但是光說不做出實際表現的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛一聽說姐姐要來也太焦慮了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}一般心不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}智乃也是 明明近來跟心愛玩得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}紗路你是在擔心心愛和智乃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我只是覺得心愛應該更自信一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那紗路也要拿出自信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:20:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}啊？ 怎麼說到我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}我很擔心紗路你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}為什麼要擔心我啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}闊別一年的再會嗎 應該很期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}又期待又擔憂吧 連那個心愛都慌成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}作為姐姐的成長嗎？ 真是自尋煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}那種東西 只要是親人 無須刻意展示也能感受得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}你偶爾也會說些正經話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}這裡也有個自大的兒子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}差不多到車站了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}不去接真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}她信裡說會自己來店裡的 叫心愛專心工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}是這樣的吧？ 心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心…愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.05,0:21:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}心愛緊張得僵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喂 你還得接客呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}信裡不是叫你專心工作的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.89,0:21:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be3}喂 喂 心愛 沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be3}心愛的姐姐…是個怎樣的人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4\bord0\c&H8AD6D9&\frz51.482\frx8\fry4\pos(734,252)}變\N成\N兔\N子\N的\N咖\N啡\N師\N傅
